      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "なんだかとっても楽しそうにしてるから\nどこに行くのか、気になって……",
      "startTime": 64.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.517873605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あはは……私、そんなに分かりやすかったかな～",
      "startTime": 67.517873605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.8845402717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik008.m4a",
      "text": "（ど、どうしよう！？　事実をそのまま伝える……！？）\n（ダメダメ、誰にも言ったことないのに……！）",
      "startTime": 76.7512041252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.3512069384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "じー……",
      "startTime": 80.3512069384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.8167852163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik009.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、雫ちゃん？\nそんなに見つめられると照れるんだけど……",
      "startTime": 85.3501157364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.6501185496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか梨子ちゃんは……私と同じ匂いがする",
      "startTime": 88.6501185496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.8656053941
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
