      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっと、つかぬことをお聞きしますが……\n雫ちゃんも、その……壁、とか……好きなの？",
      "startTime": 104.2989359142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.4322751125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "壁……？　壁サークル、的な……？\n……なるほど、梨子ちゃんはそっちの沼なんだ、ね……",
      "startTime": 114.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.3584290903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik013.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ、うーん……\nま、まぁ、そんなところかしら！",
      "startTime": 120.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.6917624236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "私はドルオタだけど、大丈夫\nジャンルは違っても、私達は仲間",
      "startTime": 127.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.0944831928
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik014.m4a",
      "text": "……詳しいこと、聞かなくていいの？",
      "startTime": 131.0944831928,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "オタクの趣味は、千差万別……\n話したいものも、そうでないものもある……",
      "startTime": 137.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.3358887117
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私は……梨子ちゃんの領域には\n無断で立ち入らないから、安心して……",
      "startTime": 144.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1825553656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rik",
      "speakerName": "桜内梨子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rik.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rik_01_01-rik015.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん……",
